Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.39,0:22:33.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Todos sorriem para garotas bonitas
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.73,0:22:34.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Meu Sonho!)
Dialogue: 2,0:22:35.61,0:22:37.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Só quero saber o que o futuro guarda
Dialogue: 2,0:22:37.53,0:22:38.15,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Sozinha!)
Dialogue: 2,0:22:38.15,0:22:42.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Mesmo que as estrelas em um céu sem lua
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.61,0:22:44.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}ainda brilhem
