Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.87,0:22:49.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Mesmo que as nuvens em um céu sem sol
Dialogue: 2,0:22:49.66,0:22:52.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}ainda sigam seu caminho
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.46,0:22:54.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Eu continuo tristemente
Dialogue: 2,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Que parecia que sempre ficaria ao meu lado)
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.67,0:22:58.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}a procurar por você
Dialogue: 2,0:22:58.51,0:23:02.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Vou enquadrar uma foto de nós dois e pendurar
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.43,0:23:06.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Vou organizar tudo do meu jeito, como eu quiser, como realmente é
Dialogue: 2,0:23:06.76,0:23:10.18,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Nossa sintonia: somar, subtrair, multiplicar, dividir por...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.18,0:23:10.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Eu amo tudo isso!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.93,0:23:14.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Me chamando, te chamando
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.27,0:23:15.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(E Você)
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.40,0:23:17.94,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Quero subir as escadas do futuro com você
Dialogue: 2,0:23:17.94,0:23:20.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6\i1}Lucky lucky shiny{\i0}, nossos corações vibrando em sonhos
Dialogue: 2,0:23:20.78,0:23:24.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Se amanhã o céu estiver limpo, vai ficar tudo bem
Dialogue: 2,0:23:24.95,0:23:28.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Talvez eu esteja um pouco triste e fraco
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.41,0:23:29.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Mas Feliz!)
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.41,0:23:32.25,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Mas quando estou com você, me sinto salva
Dialogue: 2,0:23:32.25,0:23:34.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Não existe tempo perdido
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.08,0:23:36.42,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}Vamos esperar a chuva passar
