Dialogue: 2,0:23:42.88,0:23:43.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}(Essa é a prova!)
Dialogue: 2,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.6}É isso que nos conecta
